      "text": "To the chief Musician, A Psalm of David. In thee, O LORD, do I put my trust; let me never be ashamed: deliver me in thy righteousness.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 31:1",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA031.htm",
      "text": "For the Chief Musician. A Psalm of David. In thee, O Jehovah, do I take refuge; Let me never be put to shame: Deliver me in thy righteousness.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 31:1",
